</div>

<div class="row-2  col-1">

<div class="cell-0 val-category val-date section-category"><p class="A" id="id2020-09-28---games">2020/09/28 - <a href="/category/games">games</a></p></div>

</div>

<div class="row-3  col-1">

<div class="cell-0 val-content "><p class="" id="idBitcoin-payments">Bitcoin payments</p><p class="" id="idFinally--It-s-here--Bitcoin-micropayment">Finally! It’s here. Bitcoin micropayments using lnbits.com API. This is exciting for server administrators because they can attract players with rewards in bitcoin. It only takes a few extra seconds to join a match, and each player can pay into the game and the winner gets the payout. This would be fun to take a cut to pay content creators too. There are lots of directions this could go.</p><style>
#id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-25-20at-2012-57:before {background-image: url("/Screen Shot 2020-09-25 at 12.57-final.jpg");}</style><p class="IMG" id="id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-25-20at-2012-57"><img src="/Screen Shot 2020-09-25 at 12.57-final.jpg" alt="quakejs bitcoin"></p><style>
#id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-22-20at-2010-21:before {background-image: url("/Screen Shot 2020-09-22 at 10.21.04 AM-final.jpg");}</style><p class="IMG" id="id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-22-20at-2010-21"><img src="/Screen Shot 2020-09-22 at 10.21.04 AM-final.jpg" alt="bitcoin settings"></p><style>
#id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-23-20at-205-27-:before {background-image: url("/Screen Shot 2020-09-23 at 5.27.49 PM-final.jpg");}</style><p class="IMG" id="id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-23-20at-205-27-"><img src="/Screen Shot 2020-09-23 at 5.27.49 PM-final.jpg" alt="payment required"></p><p class="" id="idI-think-I-might-also-have-a-fix-for-thes">I think I might also have a fix for these lightmaps showing up incorrectly the first time it loads.</p><style>
#id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-27-20at-204-11-:before {background-image: url("/Screen Shot 2020-09-27 at 4.11.30 PM-final.jpg");}</style><p class="IMG" id="id-Screen-20Shot-202020-09-27-20at-204-11-"><img src="/Screen Shot 2020-09-27 at 4.11.30 PM-final.jpg" alt="wrong lightmaps"></p><p class="" id="idVersus">Versus</p><style>
#idScreen-20Shot-202020-09-27-20at-204-12-3:before {background-image: url("Screen Shot 2020-09-27 at 4.12.35 PM-final.jpg");}</style><p class="IMG" id="idScreen-20Shot-202020-09-27-20at-204-12-3"><img src="Screen Shot 2020-09-27 at 4.12.35 PM-final.jpg" alt="reloaded lightmaps"></p><p class="A A" id="idI-figured-out-I-can-use-interpreted-QVMs">I figured out I can use interpreted QVMs instead of WASM for <a href="https://caniuse.com/asmjs">ASM.js</a> builds. And I should have a WebGL fallback to Canvas + <a href="https://github.com/h0MER247/swGL">Software GL</a> pretty soon. This will expand the number of devices it is playable on greatly, including my old iPad 1!</p><p class="" id="idI-will-fix-pure-server-connections-by-sp">I will fix pure server connections by spoofing the checksums from known paks. This isn’t necessarily less secure, since I am verifying repacked checksums also, but it will be really fun to be able to play on any server, not just QuakeJS servers!</p></div>

